<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title><%= tool.name %> | AIDEX</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>

<div class="tool-container">

<div class="tool-card">

<!-- TOOL LOGO (NEW ADDITION) -->
<% if(tool.logo){ %>
<div class="tool-logo-wrapper">
<img src="<%= tool.logo %>" alt="<%= tool.name %> Logo" class="tool-logo-large">
</div>
<% } %>

<h1 class="tool-title">
<%= tool.name %>
</h1>

<% if(tool.trending){ %>
<span class="trending-badge">🔥 Trending Tool</span>
<% } %>

<p class="tool-category">
Category: <strong><%= tool.category %></strong>
</p>

<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->
<p class="tool-description">
<%= tool.description %>
</p>

<!-- EXTRA INFO SECTION (NEW UPGRADE) -->
<div class="tool-extra-info">

<h3>About this AI Tool</h3>

<p>
<%= tool.name %> is one of the popular tools in the <strong><%= tool.category %></strong> category.
It helps users improve productivity using artificial intelligence and modern automation technology.
Many professionals, creators, and developers use this tool to simplify complex tasks and work faster.
</p>

<p>
AIDEX helps you discover tools like <%= tool.name %> so you can explore the best AI platforms available today.
Click the button below to visit the official website and start using it.
</p>

</div>

<div class="tool-buttons">

<a href="<%= tool.url %>" target="_blank" class="visit-btn">
Visit Official Website
</a>

<a href="/tools" class="back-btn">
← Back to Tools
</a>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
